Comment: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛…你还没睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧…马纳多你喝酒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喝了一点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你可以喝酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,广场附近的花园街有家名为雪莉的酒馆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一直是义勇兵的聚集地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在那里打听些情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能为了我们做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对一穷二白的我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,酒钱可一点儿也不便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…我们还是快就适应这样的生活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得 很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我们睡觉的时候你还…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我打算换个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有个地方我们能应付过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能带我一起去酒馆就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛能喝酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…不知道呢 我有喝过酒的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不觉得讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可能有着想喝的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下次要是大家能一起去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是呢 那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,盗贼公会怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还是比较辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老师太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是个美女 但太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老师是个满脸胡子的肌肉男
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,严厉不说 嗓门还大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喊得我耳朵都疼 挺遭罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎样被骂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,记不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我都在想是不是自己生来就是要挨骂的主了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在被骂中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多你也有这种时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有的啊 还不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮很红呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并不知道这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道我们是从什么地方 怎样来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 有一点可以确定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不属于这里的某个地方 上空的月亮不会是红的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,红月亮什么的…太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,发现哥布林了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有了 就一只
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,单独行动的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,武器呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能有冰块之类的让我冷静一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么大喊就没有偷袭的意义了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的  梦儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在跟谁战斗啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊 结果还是我最先到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很不像盗贼的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击范围差距太大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有了 割他手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太浅了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,动作千万别停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恶殷红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,玛莉姆·爱姆·帕鲁酷！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索 去哥布林的正面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大家把他包围住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索 给他施加压力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,压力啊压力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.38,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Just like a soldier I'll be hunting for the prey
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.26,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Thought it be easy But I might need to pray
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.11,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Rage gotta step aside Focus gotta stay alive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.00,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Wassup wanna die Victory's all mine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.68,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Whether you like it or not Here's the truth don't eva eva look back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.63,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Stay gold for you You're not alone You're got your team too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.13,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Sky is the limit so raise your spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.89,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}In a cold dark forest Finding what I wanted Feeling the speed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.29,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Hurry No more time to waste and lie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.56,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}A big blowing wind drifting Like a water stream
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.73,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Never gonna sleep again
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.48,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Find a way to beat the vain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.31,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Drain the blood into the sword  Cut the evil with the stroke
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.32,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}Mighty mighty heart I want  With my dagger here I come
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.38,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}正如一个战士一般 我搜寻着猎食的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.26,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}还以为这会很轻松 而我需要祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.11,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}愤怒也会走向一旁 专注才会有机会活下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.00,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}怎么了 想死吗 胜利只属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.68,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}不管你喜不喜欢 这就是事实 请不要回头留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.63,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}依然做最好的自己 你并不孤单 你有自己的团队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.13,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}天空就是你的舞台 请重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.89,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}在冰冷黑暗的森林 寻找我所想要一切 感受这速度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.29,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}赶快 不要再浪费时间说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.56,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}飓风肆意的吹拂 就如水流一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.73,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}不会再次沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.48,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}找寻抵抗空虚的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.31,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}刀剑下流干的血 将恶魔击败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.32,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\fsp3\an8}我渴望坚强的心 带着匕首 我再次启程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚插到了骨头…骨头的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哥布林也在拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被杀 岂能被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被干掉之前先干掉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然听不懂他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能感觉到他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可别害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要么杀要么被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这货干掉 积累恶德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的腿可是不停在发软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,少废话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哥布林 还真是顽强啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,玛莉姆·爱姆·帕鲁酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,打中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我做到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,史卡勒海尔大人啊！您刚才看见了吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}哈尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢拔出来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,光啊 以卢米埃里斯庇护的名义下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,战利品的话…就这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似是某个动物的牙？ 这个是银币？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 为了积累恶德值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要通过暗黑骑士了结他的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后将一部分肉体献给到公会里的祭坛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵太大了….那就用爪子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉他的可是莫古索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 莫古索你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把我值得纪念的第一份恶德给抢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个的话值30个铜币
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是银币哦 虽然稍微脏了些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个缺角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去别的家问问价也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不过到哪里都会是这个价位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那颗牙齿是黑狼的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得1个银币合适的话 我就买下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗牙值这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可以当做辟邪道具的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,时间还早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就暂时休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,确实累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那今天就在这里解散
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:22.33,kashi,,0,0,0,,窓から見える淡い光が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:28.95,kashi,,0,0,0,,優しく頬を照らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:34.51,kashi,,0,0,0,,どこかで君も見ているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:41.92,kashi,,0,0,0,,この空の下繋がってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:11.79,kashi,,0,0,0,,さわめく木の叶　緑の匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:18.85,kashi,,0,0,0,,街の真ん中一人きりで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:23.92,kashi,,0,0,0,,廻る季節を感じてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:29.02,kashi,,0,0,0,,変わり映えのない日々
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:35.98,kashi,,0,0,0,,広い世界に投げ出されたようで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:41.57,kashi,,0,0,0,,思わず下を向いたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:48.11,kashi,,0,0,0,,小さな命の声を聴いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:58.90,kashi,,0,0,0,,ほら一人じゃないから大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:11.74,kashi,,0,0,0,,きっと目を閉じてたら気付けない事が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.53,kashi,,0,0,0,,たくさんあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:23.81,kashi,,0,0,0,,怖がらないで少しで良いから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:32.09,kashi,,0,0,0,,まだあどけない勇気で踏み出して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:49.57,kashi,,0,0,0,,何気ない事　繰り返す日々で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:56.19,kashi,,0,0,0,,交わす言葉は意味もなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:01.46,kashi,,0,0,0,,だけど確かに教えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:07.19,kashi,,0,0,0,,繋がっている事を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:13.47,kashi,,0,0,0,,ふとした時に心で感じたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:19.09,kashi,,0,0,0,,予想もつかない未来は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:25.65,kashi,,0,0,0,,突然訪ねる前触れもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:30.75,kashi,,0,0,0,,もう一人じゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:39.30,kashi,,0,0,0,,きっと心の奥で芽吹いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:43.94,kashi,,0,0,0,,この暖かな気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:48.13,kashi,,0,0,0,,焦らなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:55.43,kashi,,0,0,0,,一つ一つずつ育てて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:17:01.64,kashi,,0,0,0,,共に在る軌跡を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:32.63,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}いつかこの手を放すその時がきても
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.47,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:48.17,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}気つけば傍に君がいることを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.43,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}幸せにおもうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:59.88,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}小さな奇跡出会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:08.11,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}きっかけはもう覚えてないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:22.33,kashi,,0,0,0,,微弱的光芒 从窗外映入眼帘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:28.95,kashi,,0,0,0,,温柔地照拂在脸颊上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:34.51,kashi,,0,0,0,,不知在世界何处的你 是不是也在看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:41.92,kashi,,0,0,0,,我们在这片天空下相连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:11.79,kashi,,0,0,0,,沙沙作响的树叶 散发出新绿的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:18.85,kashi,,0,0,0,,在这个城市的正中央 独自一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:23.92,kashi,,0,0,0,,季节的更替 我一直都感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:29.02,kashi,,0,0,0,,平平淡淡没有改变的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:35.98,kashi,,0,0,0,,如同被这个广阔的世界所抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:41.57,kashi,,0,0,0,,每当不知不觉垂下了头 灰心丧气的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:48.11,kashi,,0,0,0,,听着身边渺小的一个个生命发出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:58.90,kashi,,0,0,0,,你瞧 你并不是孤独一人哦 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:11.74,kashi,,0,0,0,,如果闭上双眼那就一定会错过身边发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.53,kashi,,0,0,0,,许许多多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:23.81,kashi,,0,0,0,,不用感到害怕 只需要一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:32.09,kashi,,0,0,0,,再鼓起一点点天真的勇气踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:49.57,kashi,,0,0,0,,波澜不惊 不断重复的平淡的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:56.19,kashi,,0,0,0,,连彼此交谈的话语也都没有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:01.46,kashi,,0,0,0,,但正是这样的日子在告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:07.19,kashi,,0,0,0,,我们相连在一起的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:13.47,kashi,,0,0,0,,在不经意之间 内心感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:19.09,kashi,,0,0,0,,那无法预知的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:25.65,kashi,,0,0,0,,毫无预兆地突然到访
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:30.75,kashi,,0,0,0,,已经 不再是孤独一人咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:39.30,kashi,,0,0,0,,这份温暖的心绪 在内心深处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:43.94,kashi,,0,0,0,,一定是即将慢慢萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:48.13,kashi,,0,0,0,,不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:55.43,kashi,,0,0,0,,一步一步 不断地去渐渐画下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:17:01.64,kashi,,0,0,0,,我们共同生活的轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:32.63,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}若有一天到了不得不放开手之时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.47,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}也请不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:48.17,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}意识到了身边有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.43,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}那便是幸福的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:59.88,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}能够邂逅这样小小的奇迹 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:08.11,kashi,,0,0,0,,{\an7}虽然我们已经记不起 相逢的契机是什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是有点儿暗黑骑士的风范了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啧…好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说连骨头都要吃掉的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是吹毛求疵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一个都不落下地说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没有说一个都不落下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚不就在说嘛 一个都不落下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这样不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也积累了第一份恶德值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,积累恶德值能干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可以召唤出恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个恶魔能干点儿什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果敌人靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,它就会悄悄告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔还会开些恶魔的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就这点儿事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这点儿事是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是跟本大爷我很合得来的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 跟你很相配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道恶魔能起到什么作用这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很像你那性格的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的是你…莫非你会变身技能？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只是觉得夕阳无限好就观赏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,之后这家伙就跳了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢 说的也是 别吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你慌个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,确实很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然每天我都会路过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但之前都不曾有精力去欣赏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多 你还醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,醒着呢 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我总觉得有很多事情需要跟马纳多商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说今天挣到的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人18铜币
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这样之后就真的没问题了吗…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可是事情一到嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就不好开口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,总之今天我们干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,未来的事情谁也不会晓得的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,明天或许会有更好的事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,总之现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我稍稍出去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德？ 你还醒着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,出去一趟…是去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是去澡堂啊 澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？你刚刚不是去过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且现在可是女生入浴的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个迟钝的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还没明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你…不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神确实是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是作为一个人来说干那种事很糟糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,本大爷我可是一直都很精神的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,超有精神的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,连自己都压抑不住的热火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫热情之火 熊熊燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的本能才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪你有把澡堂的墙壁细心调查了一番…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在女孩子们可都是裸露着肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在洗着身体头发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好好想象一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,男子汉该做的事情不就只有一件嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是鬼畜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请叫我鬼畜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,提高些逼格 叫我鬼畜大王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 今天我们可是越过一条界线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们得明白啊 别让我都说出来 好羞耻的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟那是两码事好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,作为人真的可以越过这条线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德参上！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德君？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德你个白痴恶心色魔变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哪凉快死哪去 永远不要再回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,最后连我们都被牵连进来 低头道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德个白痴
